snippet: President Nicos Anastasiades suggested that actions of the bank governor, Panicos O. Demetriades, led to the resignations of three central bank board members on Friday.
lead_paragraph: President Nicos Anastasiades suggested that actions of the bank governor, Panicos O. Demetriades, led to the resignations of three central bank board members on Friday.
